PROPERTY TAX -- ORANGE COUNTY; PROPOSITION 90 (PROPERTY ASSESSMENT TRANSFER); 
AGED; HOUSING -- CALIFORNIA; HOUSING SALES; PROPERTY ASSESSMENT 
</P>
