<P>
Profile 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
SHER, ABBY; SANTA MONICA MUSEUM OF ART; SANTA MONICA (CA) -- DEVELOPMENT AND 
REDEVELOPMENT; ARTS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; MUSEUMS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
